🌱 EcoHarvest – Smart Agriculture Management System

**EcoHarvest** is a user-friendly and responsive static website designed to promote a smart agriculture and crop monitoring solution. Built with pure HTML and CSS, this project showcases a clean, modern interface ideal for portfolios, client presentations, or startup landing pages.

---Main website https://www.ecoharvest.farm/

## 📌 Project Overview

The website includes:

- An engaging homepage with project highlights  
- About section detailing the mission and technology  
- Features section to outline key benefits  
- Visual gallery for agriculture or product images  
- Contact form (front-end only)  
- Fully responsive design optimized for all devices  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

| Technology     | Description                            |
|----------------|----------------------------------------|
| HTML5          | Markup for page structure              |
| CSS3           | Styling and responsive layout design   |
| Google Fonts   | Custom font for branding and style     |
| Font Awesome   | Icons for features, contact, and social|
